Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:58.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}宇宙の航路は風に消え
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:58.65,OP,NTP,0,164,0,,{\be1\fs16}そら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:02:01.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}安住は幾億光年先
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:05.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}突き進むなら惑うな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:08.41,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}いざ征かん 騎士よ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:12.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}打ち砕け KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA
